+| T1: /status via Matrix | | | | |
+| T2: Task-Erstellung | | | | |
+| T3: Approval | | | | |
+| T4: Attachment | | | | |
+| T5: Alert bei Ausfall | | | | |
+| T6: Kein Bridge-Loop | | | | |
